    <defName>ZhthyhlDredge</defName>
    <title>dredge</title>
    <titleShort>dredge</titleShort>
    <baseDescription>[PAWN_nameDef] lives on scraps. [PAWN_pronoun] at the bottom living every day on the line.</baseDescription>

